<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8209459>
    dc:description "FIGURE 16. Varitrella (Cantotrella) bakeri ♁ calling song: oscillograms showing two echemes (A) and one echeme (B); spectrogram of the same echeme (C); power spectra of a syllable (D) where the grey line represents the power [dB] (axis name and scale in grey) and the black solid peak represents the relative amplitude (axis name in black)." ;
